title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 356: Featuring Brandon Tanev
description:
On Episode 356 of Spittin’ Chiclets the guys are joined by Brandon Tanev. Brandon joined (1:42:03) to discuss what it’s like to play for the 32nd franchise, the Seattle Kraken. He also discussed not playing hockey from the ages of 15-19, his famous headshot, his brother and tons more. The guys open the show talking about Biz’s TNT debut and touch on the opening of the NHL season. With all the extensions this past week, the guys broke down all the money dished out and what they thought of the contracts. The boys wrap up talking about Youth hockey refs, golf, the NFL and more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
